Amazon Letters Tutor includes extracted Markdown copies of Amazon shareholder
letters for study, retrieval, and citation-oriented analysis.

The source letter text is credited to Amazon.com, Inc. and Jeffrey P. Bezos and
was extracted from official Amazon-hosted shareholder letter PDFs listed in
`data/SOURCES.md`.

